    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "College has one of the best infrastructure in whole DU and good campus Life",
          "name": "NITESH KUMAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "It has great research centre and profesor are well experienced",
          "name": "NITESH KUMAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The course are modified keeping in mind the ever-changing industry",
          "name": "NITESH KUMAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Supportive teachers and they have great knowledge of subject and also very friendly in nature",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lab staff were also very well mannered and cooperative",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Ectra ciricular activites and fest are amazing of my college in south campus",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College location is so prime it's near dhaul kuan and you can visit any place easily",
          "name": "Lakshay Panwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The best thing according to me is the rank of the college which is 6th over all india. Because the research and alumni network network is very nice.",
          "name": "Krishna Dangra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The canteen area is so nice and the sitting area is the best",
          "name": "Chirag kamra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "It doesn't offer a auditorium which is in construction",
          "name": "NITESH KUMAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "It doesn't provide hostel facilities for coming far away",
          "name": "NITESH KUMAR",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Students politics is so much in college which is not good for students enviroment",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Timmings of labs were very long. Science students get free from lab near 5pm in the evening",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Administrative department is too lazy in helping students in case of marksheet and degree related issues",
          "name": "Sparsh dhiman",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "College canteen is not so good food quality is bad",
          "name": "Lakshay Panwar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no air conditioner is boys common which makes hard to sit there",
          "name": "Chirag kamra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Library is small it easily get filled in short time",
          "name": "Chirag kamra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Maintaince of the sports equipments are very bad",
          "name": "Sakshi hansda",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
